snippet.title: Windjammers 2 - Release date trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Windjammers 2 on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1114290/Windjammers_2/

Windjammers 2 is bringing frenetic matches of power disc-slinging action to PC, PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch, Xbox Game Pass & Xbox Game Pass for PC on January 20, 2022. Windjammers 2 will also host showdowns on PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X|S via backward compatibility.

The release date joins Windjammers 2’s returning superstars and champions in the making for bouts of the game’s energizing head-to-head battles. Catch Windjammers 2’s roster of 10 playable athletes in action, a glimpse of the 10 varied courts they’ll be battling to score on.

Slam into all things Windjammers 2 by checking the official discord (https://discord.com/invite/2kmdubA) as well as following @Windjammers and @Dotemu on Twitter.
